title: Eyetsa Live Well
typeOfFood: Ovo, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant and fashion store founded by two sisters. Before or after shopping you can sit and enjoy a meal, fresh juices & smoothies (with cashew milk) made with fruit and/or vegetables. Some salads and soups are offered as meals such as local jollof rice and a creamy black-eyed pea variety of hummus.
